Collect from Rogelio M Dimaandal Construction and FRAGERR Construction the additional liquidated damages amounting to P21,946.44 and P3,913.53, respectively;
Submit the approved suspension order for the project Upgrading/Reconstruction of Tuguegarao City Don Domingo Public Market (Temporary Stalls-Relocation Site).  In the absence of the same, the percentage of completion of the project at the date of the original contract completion date is requested for the computation of the liquidated damages; and
Repair the damaged roofing and joining/splice of gutter for the project Repair of Barangay Gymnasium and to repair the leaking Roof Slab of the classrooms in Cataggaman National High School and Linao National High School.
